OL,3,CPoliticians 'confident' for a Guernsey-
OL,4,Conly ferry service
OL,6,FPoliticians say they are 'confident'
OL,7,Fthat a Guernsey-only service can meet
OL,8,Fits passenger and freight needs.
OL,10,FIt comes after Guernsey named Brittany
OL,11,FFerries as their chosen provider for
OL,12,Ftheir sea services.
OL,14,FThe statement comes after Guernsey's
OL,15,FCommittee for Economic Development
OL,16,Fsays they have been "encouraged" by
OL,17,Fcontinued discussions with Brittany
OL,18,FFerries in recent days.
