OL,3,CPoliticians 'confident' for a Guernsey-
OL,4,Conly ferry service
OL,6,FHowever, there are concerns over the
OL,7,Fefficiency of a Guernsey-only
OL,8,Foperator, with Jersey accounting for
OL,9,Ftwo-thirds of current ferry business.
OL,11,FOriginally, politicians from both
OL,12,FJersey and Guernsey were working
OL,13,Ftoward a joint agreement on which
OL,14,Fferry service should cater for the
OL,15,FBailiwicks.
