OL,3,CPoliticians 'confident' for a Guernsey-
OL,4,Conly ferry service
OL,6,FThe President of the Committee for
OL,7,FEconomic Development explains: "We
OL,8,Fhave made good progress in our
OL,9,Fdiscussions with Brittany Ferries
OL,10,Fsince we announced it as our preferred
OL,11,Fbidder on 30 October.
OL,13,F"Based on those discussions, we are
OL,14,Fconfident that it can run a Guernsey-
OL,15,Fonly service that meets our needs `
OL,16,Fsubject to further negotiations on
OL,17,Fsome elements.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
