OL,3,CPoliticians 'confident' for a Guernsey-
OL,4,Conly ferry service
OL,6,F"Jersey's decision is a matter for
OL,7,Fthat island. I will respect whatever
OL,8,Fdecision it reaches, while of course
OL,9,Fbeing naturally disappointed if it's
OL,10,Fnot joining us with a single provider.
OL,12,F"The provider we selected, Brittany
OL,13,FFerries, was selected based on the
OL,14,Fjoint tender that we ran with Jersey
OL,15,Fin accordance with the published
OL,16,Fprocurement documents."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
