OL,3,CPoliticians 'confident' for a Guernsey-
OL,4,Conly ferry service
OL,6,FAn exasperation between both islands
OL,7,Fappears evident, with Deputy Inder
OL,8,Fclaiming that an "inaccurate
OL,9,Fnarrative" has been presented about
OL,10,Fthe breakdown in the joint tender
OL,11,Fprocess.
OL,13,FHe explains: "We didn't break away
OL,14,Ffrom the process, we followed it
OL,15,Fthroughout and a preferred bidder
OL,16,Fneeded to be selected.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
