OL,3,CPoliticians 'confident' for a Guernsey-
OL,4,Conly ferry service
OL,6,F"We delivered the certainty our island
OL,7,Fdeserves and only did so after giving
OL,8,FJersey two weeks' notice of our
OL,9,Fintention following the closure of the
OL,10,Fscoring by both islands."
OL,12,FThere have been concerns about how
OL,13,Fviable the routes are with Jersey
OL,14,Ftaken out of the equation.
OL,16,FJersey accounts for two-thirds of the
OL,17,Fcurrent business - and even with that,
OL,18,Fthis is a sub-optimal route, so things
OL,19,Fare tight.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
