OL,3,CPoliticians 'confident' for a Guernsey-
OL,4,Conly ferry service
OL,6,FAdd into that, an ageing fleet and
OL,7,Fmaintenance costs - together with the
OL,8,Frepayments they are making to the
OL,9,FStates of Guernsey for their #26
OL,10,Fmillion loan - and they've got some
OL,11,Ftough numbers to crunch.
OL,13,FSo perhaps this is where Jersey's
OL,14,Fcaution has stemmed from, but Guernsey
OL,15,Fappears to have every confidence.
OL,17,FJust a week ago, they confirmed that
OL,18,Fthe contract would be finalised within
OL,19,F10 days and that schedules would be
OL,20,Fpublished in mid-November.
